{"tid":2319512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會廣場的國旗早上一度被倒掛","createTime":"2020-12-10T06:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T07:00:25.000Z","uid":75612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4339f8a7e32b3f640d1a8ea1f03ea30e866f980","tid":2319512,"uid":75612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:56:52.000Z","msg":"立法會廣場的國旗早上一度被倒掛，秘書處發現後糾正，並就事件鄭重致歉。秘書處表示，立法會廣場每天早上8時都會進行升旗儀式，秘書處今早知道國旗倒掛後，已在9時54分糾正。 秘書處表示，正深入調查事件，會按照內部人事管理機制嚴肅跟進，亦已檢視及改善升旗程序，確保同類事情不再發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76983e24904d332386093a20208d3d9891e9ec6c","tid":2319512,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:59:24.000Z","msg":"係咪國安署接手案件?"},{"pid":"e18ef4dfc775ae215112a4f0b66fd481a3496c10","tid":2319512,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"升旗手前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}